13:55.500 --> 13:59.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Is that your sense of what's
happening, that you're going
to get maybe a better treatment

14:00.666 --> 14:02.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
