very productive discussion
with the president with
some of our leadership

14:10.933 --> 14:15.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
earlier in the year, and
I think the president's
focused on two things.

14:15.033 --> 14:19.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
One is ensuring that we
continue to lead the world in
developing better treatments and

14:19.166 --> 14:24.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
cures and, two, on
jobs, ensuring that
we have more domestic
investment in the United

14:26.000 --> 14:27.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
States.

14:27.966 --> 14:30.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think our industry
