on both those fronts.

14:30.066 --> 14:35.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our industry spends $70
billion a year in research and
development, which is more than

14:35.800 --> 14:37.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
