15:02.533 --> 15:04.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What is going on?

15:04.333 --> 15:06.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
What do you see is
the problem here?

15:06.666 --> 15:11.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
STEPHEN UBL: Well, I
should start by trying
to make sure that we're
on the same fact basis.

15:11.600 --> 15:16.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, if you look at Express
Scripts, which is a leading
PBM in the industry, pharmacy

15:18.500 --> 15:22.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
benefit manager, looking
at spending in 2016, drug
spending went up 3.5 percent.

15:23.700 --> 15:26.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
