three years, prescription
drug spending was actually
the lowest growing

15:32.900 --> 15:36.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
or slowest growing
category in health care.

15:36.000 --> 15:41.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
