2014 and 2015, I would argue,
due to some anomalous factors.

15:42.100 --> 15:45.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
FDA approved a
number of new drugs.

15:45.733 --> 15:48.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Medicaid was expanded.

15:48.066 --> 15:52.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
