the treatment of that

15:54.133 --> 15:57.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
disease and will obviate the
need for liver transplant, as
well as reduce the incidence

15:58.400 --> 15:59.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of liver cancer.

15:59.900 --> 16:03.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We're now on the back-half
of that spike, if you will.

16:03.266 --> 16:06.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The python has sort of
digested the tennis ball.

16:06.333 --> 16:11.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And even CMS' own actuaries
estimate that drug spending
will be between 4 and 6 percent

16:11.200 --> 16:15.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
for the next 10 years, which
