overall health care spending.

16:15.766 --> 16:20.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: At the same
time, a lot of finger-pointing
going on in the health care

16:20.700 --> 16:25.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
industry between the drug
