managers, hospitals, insurers.

16:27.666 --> 16:31.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A lot of those fingers
are being pointed, though,
still at your industry.

16:31.400 --> 16:36.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHEN UBL: We think
there are -- we take these
issues very seriously.

16:36.366 --> 16:41.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we think there are
pragmatic, consumer-oriented
solutions to address
some of the issues that

16:41.100 --> 16:43.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
have been raised.

16:43.133 --> 16:47.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, for example, a lot of the
media attention in the last year
is focused on companies that

16:48.266 --> 16:50.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
