16:56.700 --> 17:00.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we think there are
policy solutions, primarily
at the FDA, that would
address those situations.

17:02.266 --> 17:05.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Similarly, we think, as
an industry, the pricing
model needs to evolve.

17:05.700 --> 17:09.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We need to move away from
paying for volume to paying
for the value of care.

17:09.900 --> 17:14.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And I was reading
that's what the administration
is -- among the things

17:14.300 --> 17:16.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the administration
is looking at.

17:16.333 --> 17:18.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I have also read, though,
that the critics look at that
and say that, in the end, it

17:18.966 --> 17:23.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
may work for some people, but
