negotiations with Medicare
over the price of drugs?

18:18.366 --> 18:21.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHEN UBL: I think there's
been a little bit of clinical
trial on this question.

18:21.700 --> 18:26.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you look at countries that
have adopted models like the
VA on a broad scale, the U.K.,

18:28.766 --> 18:32.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
