is that patients have less
access to novel therapies.

18:34.300 --> 18:36.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we think that would be a
movement in the wrong direction.

18:36.733 --> 18:41.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So the VA, keep in mind, is a
closed system, a small number,
relatively small number of

18:42.466 --> 18:44.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
hospitals and consumers.

18:44.433 --> 18:49.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
