plans, again, to try to achieve
some specific metrics tied

19:06.766 --> 19:11.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to patient outcomes and then
be reimbursed on a differential
basis based on whether the

19:11.500 --> 19:13.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
patient actually
achieves those outcomes.

19:13.433 --> 19:15.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Finally, opioids.

