minimizing or even trivializing

19:40.166 --> 19:42.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the impact.

19:42.266 --> 19:46.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How do you, as someone who
sits in such a responsible
position, look at this?

19:48.433 --> 19:51.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHEN UBL: I can assure you
that -- speaking personally on
behalf of the industry, that

19:51.900 --> 19:56.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
no one trivializes the crisis
that we're facing in this
country around opioids.

19:58.666 --> 20:02.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But it is a
multifactorial crisis.

20:02.000 --> 20:07.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's a lot of stakeholders
that need to come
together on a solution,
prescribing physicians,

20:09.366 --> 20:13.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
