Mitch McConnell.

29:18.433 --> 29:21.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Have the
Republicans made the case that
this is something better or

29:21.766 --> 29:23.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
