version of Obamacare.

29:57.866 --> 29:59.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Mark?

29:59.400 --> 30:04.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: Two things
hit me, first of all.

30:05.966 --> 30:08.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
