no debate, no hearings,
so that's been a cry.

30:08.033 --> 30:12.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But it's interesting, because
there is no public case to
be made for the Republican

30:12.000 --> 30:14.533 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
