51:37.733 --> 51:39.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT, Chairman &amp;
CEO, Berkshire Hathaway: This
country made such a terrible

51:39.333 --> 51:41.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
